# 🚀 FlashFusion Creative Hub

> AI-powered SaaS platform for creators and business owners to generate, design, and publish e-commerce content across multiple platforms.

## ✨ Features

- 🎨 AI-powered content generation
- 🛍️ Multi-platform publishing (Shopify, Etsy, TikTok Shop, eBay)
- 🔧 Embeddable widgets for external websites
- 📊 Analytics and insights
- 👥 Dual-role system (Creators & Owners)

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/flashfusion-creative-hub.git

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npm run dev
